channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Biden's Insane Comments About Lloyd Austin, Black Neighborhoods in Trainwreck BET Interview
Trump to formally accept Republican presidential nomination in speech altered after assassination attempt
item.description: Five days after surviving an assassination attempt, former President Trump will formally accept the GOP presidential nomination during the culminating moment of the 2024 Republican National Convention

item.title: Trump Jr.: Father 'Showed America's Character' After Shot
item.description: Donald Trump showed America's character when he pumped his fist and told a Pennsylvania crowd to "fight" following the assassination attempt on his life, Donald Trump Jr. said Wednesday during an appearance at the Republican National Convention.

item.title: Operation Dump Biden Goes Into High Gear—What Pelosi Reportedly Told Him
Flashback: A look at Donald Trump's remarks at the 2016, 2020 Republican conventions
item.description: This is Trump's third Republican National Convention being named the GOP's presidential nominee. His remarks are expected to be aimed at bringing the country together after the assassination attempt against him.

item.title: VP Harris Condemns 'Cowardly' Trump Assassination Attempt
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris condemned the recent assassination attempt on former President Donald Trump at a campaign event on Wednesday, The Hill reported.

item.title: Things Do Not Go Well When Secret Service Head Kim Cheatle Shows Up at the RNC
Trump VP pick JD Vance pledges to ‘commit to the working man’ as populism takes center stage at RNC
item.description: Sen. JD Vance, Trump's running mate in the 2024 White House race, said he will be a vice president who “never forgets" where he came from while striking a populist tone at the RNC.

item.title: Kimberly Guilfoyle: God Put 'Armor of Protection' on Trump
item.description: Former California prosecutor Kimberly Guilfoyle told the crowd at the Republican National Convention in Milwaukee Wednesday that "God has put an armor of protection on Donald Trump."

item.title: WATCH: MSNBC and DNC's Complete Disrespect of Gold Star Families During Republican Convention
‘Ruined by negligence’: Dave Portnoy blasts Nantucket wind farm after broken blade shuts down beaches
item.description: Barstool Sports' Dave Portnoy is speaking out after an offshore windmill blade snapped and sent fiberglass shards onto the Nantucket shoreline.

item.title: Fmr ICE Director: Biden Border 'National Suicide'
item.description: A former acting director of Immigration and Customs Enforcement, Tom Homan, told attendees at the Republican National Convention that President Joe Biden's open border policy is "a choice." "It's national suicide," he said Wednesday night at the convention."I worked for six...

item.title: WATCH: J.D. Vance Delivers Passionate Speech at the RNC, Shows Why He's the Epitome of the American Dream
Senators confront Secret Service chief at Republican convention: ‘You owe President Trump answers’
item.description: Multiple Republican senators confronted Secret Service Director Kimberly Cheatle about the attempted assassination of former President Trump on Wednesday.

item.title: Vance Accepts VP Nod, Addresses RNC on Rural Upbringing
item.description: Sen. J.D. Vance of Ohio accepted the Republican nomination as vice president on Wednesday night in Milwaukee, focusing much of his speech on his upbringing in a rural town that "had been cast aside and forgotten by America's ruling class in Washington."
